rey-chappell-roan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/mariah-carey-chappell-roan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/mariah-carey-chappell-roan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mariah-carey">玛丽亚·凯莉 (Mariah Carey)</a>评论了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan)</a>的成名经历，承认有时“并不有趣”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/chappell-roan-live-in-london-a-joyous-celebration-of-queerness-community-and-fun-3795515">查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 伦敦现场演出：一场关于酷儿、社区和乐趣的欢乐庆典</a></strong></li></ul><p>本月早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-reveals-severe-depression-diagnosis-3795902">罗恩表示，她被诊断出患有“严重抑郁症”</a> ，她将此归因于她的名气迅速上升，她告诉<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2024/sep/20/fame-is-like-going-through-puberty-chappell-roan-on-sexuality-superstardom-and-the-joy-of-drag" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a> ，像去公园这样的正常活动现在都需要她“预订安全”并考虑“我该如何以安全的方式做到这一点，才不会被跟踪或骚扰？”</p><p>最近在接受<a href="https://apnews.com/article/mariah-carey-christmas-album-interview-eb9c627b8caac5eb8fc33138d830c133" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>美联社</em></a>采访时，流行音乐重量级人物凯里被要求为像罗恩这样突然成为聚光灯的年轻艺术家分享建议。 </p><figure id="attachment_3795517" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3795517" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3795517" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024.jpg" alt="查佩尔·罗恩（吉姆·戴森/盖蒂图片社拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3795517" class="wp-caption-text">查佩尔·罗恩（吉姆·戴森/盖蒂图片社拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p> “好吧，”凯里说，“我已经经历过一些戏剧性的事情，但这并不有趣，因为你长大后会想，‘我想出名。’”我的意思是，真的对我来说，‘我想成为一名歌手’。我想写歌。</p><p> “但是‘我想出名’就在那里，”她继续说道。 “我觉得这可能是因为我觉得自己不够好，因为我在成长过程中经历了一些事情。这可不是一种好的感觉，你知道吗？”</p><p>罗恩对名誉的感受一直成为头条新闻，她最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-fame-is-like-an-abusive-ex-husband-3794622">将其比作“虐待的前夫”</a> 。在接受<a href="https://theface.com/music/chappell-roan-pop-music-famous-interview-good-luck-babe"><em>《The Face》</em></a>采访时，这位歌手发泄了极端粉丝行为的常态化，包括“跟踪、在网上说废话、[那些人]不肯让你孤单、在公共场合对你大喊大叫”。她补充道：“我不知道感觉会这么糟糕。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_CGxsrP4Bc/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:x