聆听 The Hu 喧闹的翻唱 Iron Maiden 的《The Trooper》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-raucous-cover-of-iron-maidens-the-trooper-by-the-hu-3799914?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-胡人边的铁娘子骑兵的喧闹封面Max PilleySat, 05 Oct 2024 21:34:38 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetal https://www.nme.com/?p=3799914 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the_hu_2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="胡人" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the_hu_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the_hu_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the_hu_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the_hu_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the_hu_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the_hu_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>蒙古乐队将为铁娘子乐队当前巡演的北美站开场</p><p>帖子《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-raucous-cover-of-iron-maidens-the-trooper-by-the-hu-3799914">聆听 The Hu 喧闹的 Iron Maiden 歌曲《The Trooper》翻唱》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the_hu_2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="胡人" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the_hu_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the_hu_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the_hu_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the_hu_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the_hu_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the_hu_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>蒙古金属乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-hu">The Hu</a>发行了他们翻唱的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iron-maiden">Iron Maiden</a>的《The Trooper》，随后将加入这支标志性乐队的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-announce-2024-north-american-tour-buy-tickets-3524133">Future Past 巡演</a>。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="560" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/mongolian-metallers-the-hu-star-wars-2637404"><b>蒙古金属乐队 The Hu：“我们希望成为传奇乐队之一”</b></a></li></ul><p>乌兰巴托乐队于周五（10 月 4 日）在加利福尼亚州圣地亚哥为 Iron Maiden 进行了首场演出，并将在整个 10 月和 11 月继续与他们一起在北美巡演。</p><p>为了纪念他们参加巡演，乐队还分享了 Maiden 1983 年单曲“The Trooper”的版本，该版本最初发行在他们的第四张录音室专辑“Piece Of Mind”中。</p><p>在这里观看喧闹、令人肾上腺素飙升的封面视频： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="The HU - “The Trooper”（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2WrvFUZgHro?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>乐队主唱 Gala 表示：“The Hu 很高兴能参加 Iron Maiden 的 Future Past 北美巡演。对我们来说，这次巡演代表了蒙古音乐产业的一个重要里程碑，也是迈向世界舞台的历史性一步。作为特别的感谢，并出于对乐队粉丝的极大尊重，我们翻唱了他们的传奇歌曲“The Trooper”，并很高兴在这次巡演之前与您分享！”</p><p>除了“Future Past”巡演之外，The Hu 还将在北美各地举办一系列头条节目，其中包括嘉宾“葬礼肖像”。 <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fthe-hu-tickets%2Fartist%2F2639449" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>查找他们的美国演出门票。</p><p>该乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-hu-share-details-of-new-album-rumble-of-thunder-3265142">于 2022 年发行了第二张也是迄今为止的最新专辑“Rumble Of Thunder”</a> 。它包括单曲《Black Thunder》和《This Is Mongol》，随后于 2023 年推出了豪华版。</p><p>不过，他们确实于今年 6 月通过 Better Noise Records 发行了他们在 2023 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上</a>首次演出的现场专辑，名为“The Hu Live At Glastonbury”。该专辑还包括翻唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metallica">Metallica</a>的《Through The Never》。</p><p>他们还与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pantera">Pantera</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/disturbed">Disturbed</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lamb-of-god">Lamb Of God</a>等乐队一起参加了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/knotfest-auastralia-2024-line-up-dates-tickets-3543372">2024 年 3 月 Slipknot 的 Knotfest Australia</a> 。</p><p>帖子《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-raucous-cover-of-iron-maidens-the-trooper-by-the-hu-3799914">聆听 The Hu 喧闹的 Iron Maiden 歌曲《The Trooper》翻唱》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
